{"tid":1364263,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"為左係元朗合法悼念李鵬 我不擇手段","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:58:20.000Z","uid":276385,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"970816c2b1973c8bfafebc44e17b57fef1deb7a2","tid":1364263,"uid":276385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/H38LUhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH38LUhL.jpg&h=313a0567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見巴打想係元朗悼念李鵬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係好感動</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係警察隨時連愛國愛港悼念活動都會取締！！留意：<br />\n<em>//《公安條例》13A: (a)如屬純為有遺體的殯殮而舉行的公眾遊行，在遊行組成的至少24小時前作出//</em><br />\n要符合條例，我建議我地要<br />\n1. 召喚李鵬係我地隊伍裡面，好次唱聖詩，讓李鵬臨到我地其中，李鵬與我們同在<br />\n2. 如果叫唔到，就搵一位叫李鵬既人殯殮。佢可以<br />\n搞生前葬禮，<br />\n或者臨死之前去入境處改名，<br />\n或者學習拉撒路故事－－－<br />\n去到遊行終點，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鄺神叫：起來！</span></strong>李鵬就起來，抱著褥子走了<br />\n3. 叫李鵬飛參加，誤導警員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">李鵬係我地最偉大既領袖</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6f08e3a98b2a0d7e76ee5a3c71aced868a4343","tid":1364263,"uid":211293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"［統計］ 727元朗到底幾點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00c85341a5258308f6a30b69bc514c0c346e68b4","tid":1364263,"uid":276385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Zu3Gne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Zu3Gne.jpg&h=1e466db2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e44d90953323eb3ad8d298ac4237997b515563bb","tid":1364263,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自推<br />\n香港反對逃犯條例事件簿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1365072/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1365072/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a7610a74050f65f577fa7f5436c264478c217a6d","tid":1364263,"uid":264797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"集氣<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CuZ0AJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CuZ0AJ.jpg&h=20fef1b9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UNQZf83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUNQZf83.jpg&h=cee05d93&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5K3HO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5K3HO4.jpg&h=0a086bdc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}